metadata.description:
Round, and round, and round he goes. And where he stops, nobody knows. Another king-of-secrets artist delivers a freaky slab of funk that kicks somewhere between Squarepusher, Funki Porcini, and someone else we can't quite place.

That's right, sportsfans, the steel drum, the jazz percussion, the weird-as-heck instrumentation, the cowbell, for pity's sake! Does none of this make any sense? Probably not, but it's nice notsense.
metadata.title: _ And The Secret Formula - The Amazing Power Of The _ [mtw015]
